Sentencas: In this paper composite supports for solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated and evaluated.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Substrates were composed of stainless steel and yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) powders mixed in different volume ratios.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Their sintering behavior (linear shrinkage, resulting porosity) and high temperature properties (oxidation resistance, electrical conductivity) were evaluated.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Based on those results the best composition for composite supports was selected and fuel cells were fabricated.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Thin YSZ electrolytes were deposited on one side of the support and sintered at 1350 degrees C in pure hydrogen, while LNF (LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3) cathodes were deposited on the top of the electrolyte and fired in situ at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The fuel cells provided power density of about 80 mWcm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: It is worth noting that this performance was achieved without adding any catalytically active phases into composite support, while at the same time the supports exhibited relatively low porosity.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: This demonstrates that stainless steel can serve as an anode active material.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Degradation of this fuel cell was fast (12%/h), nonetheless its performance seems interesting for further investigation.
Titulo: Stainless Steel/Yttria Stabilized Zirconia Composite Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
